pullRequest.body:
In this PR, we prove that `IsFiniteLength` and `Module.length â‰  âŠ¤` are equivalent, with the latter definition given in #22127 .

This PR is also part of our porting work of @erdOne 's lean3 repository about dimension theory at [here](https://github.com/erdOne/lean-AG-morphisms), but we find that the equivalent form of the lemmas he proved actually existed in mathlib (but stated in a different way), so the only thing we have to do is to prove the equivalence of these APIs.

Co-authored-by: Wanyi He @Blackfeather007 <2100017455@stu.pku.edu.cn>

- [ ] depends on: #22127
